casebody.data:
HOCKNEY & ASSO.
v.
CORNELIUS. No. 353P055. Supreme Court of North Carolina. July 6, 2005. Grady L. Balentine, Jr., Assistant Attorney General, for C. Preston Cornelius.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 5th day of July 2005 by Plaintiff for Request to Remove from Case No. 93CVS19 the Voluntary Contracts and Res-Judicata Judgments of C. Preston Cornelius and Spouse and filed in the above case with a new caption:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference this the 6th day of July 2005."
